      "Title": "Ampere.Base.IntRange",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Ampere.Base.IntRange.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">The range class represents a range of int values. Unlike other <xref href=\"Ampere.Base.IRangify%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> implementing classes,\nIntRange contains an <xref href=\"System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> of type int to enumerate through all the values between\nthe minimum and maximum ranges. By convention, both sides of the range should be inclusive values.</p>\n"
    },
